<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ege Media Publisher - Privacy Policy</title>

  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    body{
      font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(239,68,68,.18), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg,#050505 0%,#111111 45%,#1a0000 100%);
      color:#f8fafc;
      line-height:1.8;
    }

    .container{
      max-width:900px;
      margin:auto;
      padding:70px 24px;
    }

    .card{
      background:rgba(24,24,27,.82);
      border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.14);
      border-radius:28px;
      padding:42px;
      backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
      box-shadow:0 25px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    }

    h1{
      font-size:48px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
      color:#ef4444;
      letter-spacing:-1px;
    }

    .updated{
      color:#9ca3af;
      margin-bottom:34px;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    h2{
      margin-top:34px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
      font-size:26px;
      color:#f87171;
    }

    p{
      color:#d1d5db;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      font-size:17px;
    }

    ul{
      padding-left:20px;
      color:#d1d5db;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    li{
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    a{
      color:#f87171;
      text-decoration:none;
    }

    footer{
      margin-top:42px;
      padding-top:24px;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color:#9ca3af;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    @media(max-width:700px){

      h1{
        font-size:38px;
      }

      .card{
        padding:28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="updated">
      Last Updated: May 2026
    </div>

    <p>
      Ege Media Publisher (“the Application”) respects user privacy and is committed
      to protecting information processed through connected publishing services and APIs.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Collection</h2>

    <p>
      The Application may process limited account and media-related information
      required to perform authorized publishing operations and workflow automation tasks.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Authorized account access tokens</li>
      <li>Media asset URLs and image metadata</li>
      <li>Publishing board identifiers</li>
      <li>Workflow execution logs</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How Information Is Used</h2>

    <p>
      Information is used exclusively for media publishing, workflow automation,
      content organization, and secure API communication with connected services.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>

    <p>
      The Application uses secure API authentication methods and authorized access
      credentials to protect connected publishing operations and user data.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

    <p>
      The Application may interact with third-party platforms including cloud storage,
      publishing providers, and social media APIs for authorized content distribution.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>

    <p>
      The Application does not sell or distribute personal information to unauthorized
      third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>User Rights</h2>

    <p>
      Users may revoke connected application permissions at any time through the
      settings of the associated third-party platform.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>
      For privacy-related inquiries regarding Ege Media Publisher,
      please contact the application administrator.
    </p>

    <footer>
      © 2026 Ege Media Publisher. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
